12:45.164 --> 12:54.940 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Now an
investigation that uncovered
decades of sexual abuse at one
of the nation's

12:54.974 --> 13:00.713 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
elite private preparatory
schools, and the
extent to which the school
hushed it up.

13:00.746 --> 13:03.749 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Hari Sreenivasan has that story
from our New
York studios.

13:03.783 --> 13:08.721 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The report
released last
night focused on a dozen former
teachers at

13:08.754 --> 13:12.825 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the prestigious boarding school
in Connecticut,
Choate Rosemary Hall.

13:12.858 --> 13:19.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It recounts the experiences of
24 adult alumni
who were allegedly abused
between 1963 and

13:19.899 --> 13:21.667 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
2010.

13:21.700 --> 13:25.471 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Investigators said the offenses
ranged from
kissing to groping to rape.

13:25.504 --> 13:30.643 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Choate hired a law firm with no
previous ties
to the school to lead the
investigation.

13:30.676 --> 13:35.214 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Jonathan Saltzman was part of
The Boston Globe
Spotlight team that helped break
the story.

13:35.247 --> 13:39.885 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And Paul Mones is an attorney
who has represented
sexual abuse survivors at
private schools

13:39.919 --> 13:41.153 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
and other institutions.

13:41.187 --> 13:43.622 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He is not involved in any of the
Choate cases.

13:43.656 --> 13:45.524 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Jonathan, I want to start with
you.

13:45.558 --> 13:51.597 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You and your team launched this
series a while
back about this happening at
elite prep schools

13:51.630 --> 13:52.598 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in the Northeast.

13:52.631 --> 13:55.601 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What did this report reveal to
you?

13:55.634 --> 14:02.408 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JONATHAN SALTZMAN, The Boston
Globe: Well,
we had reported on about 110
private schools

14:02.441 --> 14:09.014 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
