allegations
of sexual abuse over the past 25
years.

14:09.048 --> 14:11.417 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And we mentioned Choate.

14:11.450 --> 14:18.190 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But this report was initiated in
response
to that story, and it laid out
in extremely

14:18.224 --> 14:24.230 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
graphic detail the accounts of
about 24 survivors
of abuse.

14:24.263 --> 14:30.736 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And as you said in your
introduction, some
of these are extraordinarily
graphic descriptions

14:30.769 --> 14:33.539 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
