abused kids.

14:45.317 --> 14:50.055 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That's an extraordinary number,
and we haven't
seen that before in other
schools.

14:50.089 --> 14:57.863 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then what they also did was
they essentially
owned up to the fact that they
had never reported

14:57.897 --> 15:05.704 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
