welfare authorities
in Connecticut, even though it
had been required.

15:05.738 --> 15:09.708 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: There is an
incident that
was mentioned in the report of
what would

15:09.742 --> 15:13.879 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
