15:15.681 --> 15:20.986 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the headmaster to the board
of trustees
essentially labeled it --
pointed to heavy

15:21.020 --> 15:23.956 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
drinking and inappropriate
behavior.

15:23.989 --> 15:29.161 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then we find out that the
teacher in question
was still employed as a
principal at a different

15:29.194 --> 15:30.729 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
