somewhere else.

16:14.573 --> 16:18.277 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
PAUL MONES, Sexual Abuse
Attorney: What I
found particularly, if I could
just comment

16:18.310 --> 16:24.383 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
