2002.

17:51.170 --> 17:55.174 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Paul, you have
taken on
-- your clients have taken on a
lot of different

17:55.207 --> 17:56.875 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
