Shame on you!

29:16.488 --> 29:21.960 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Republican
Senator Jeff Flake
was booed lustily during an
exchange on health

29:21.993 --> 29:23.828 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
care.

29:23.862 --> 29:32.403 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: Mr. Flake, why is it
that, in Germany,
we have had a universal health
care system

29:32.437 --> 29:33.571 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
since...

29:33.605 --> 29:37.075 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
