29:39.644 --> 29:40.612 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Since 1871?

29:40.645 --> 29:41.780 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

29:41.813 --> 29:45.717 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFF FLAKE (R), Arizona: Well,
thank you for
that.

29:45.750 --> 29:47.986 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I just -- I don't happen to
agree.

29:48.019 --> 29:49.654 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I think the free market
system...

29:49.687 --> 29:50.722 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
(BOOING)

29:50.755 --> 29:53.658 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And in South
Carolina on Monday.

29:53.691 --> 29:55.393 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

29:55.426 --> 29:58.696 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOE WILSON (R), South Carolina:
Obamacare
is denying services, delaying
services.

29:58.730 --> 30:03.401 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Representative
Joe Wilson heard
it from voters who parroted the
charge he

30:03.434 --> 30:05.670 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
once hurled at President Obama.

30:05.703 --> 30:07.305 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
AUDIENCE: You lie!

30:07.338 --> 30:08.406 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
You lie!

30:08.439 --> 30:10.341 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
You lie!

30:10.375 --> 30:15.380 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Wednesday night,
Colorado constituents
demanded that Representative
Mike Coffman

30:15.413 --> 30:17.215 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
break with President Trump.

30:17.248 --> 30:21.019 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: I would like to know when
you are going
to stop voting with the
