and start fighting
for Coloradans?

30:24.455 --> 30:25.490 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)

30:25.523 --> 30:27.158 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
