40:48.813 --> 40:50.648 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Right.

40:50.681 --> 40:52.349 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: Disadvantages if
